      "comment": "PAW GELDOFF (6) turned in a solid run last start over 425m at Bendigo finishing 4th and beaten only 2.25 lengths (24.28). Can make amends. MAXIMUM REED (7) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing third (31.18) and beaten 3 lengths over 545m at Ballarat. Expected to be in the finish again. REV IAN (2) turned in a moderate performance last time when eighth at this track over 600m behind Lamia Taya (35.14) in a R/A FIN. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. BUN QUAKE (3) must be included in calculations.",
